title: Bluetooth calling
content: My phone was working just fine all day long but as I left work and tried to make a call with my headphones I just got silence, tried going through my car and the same thing. I hear notifications and other media but not even a dial tone when I make a call. I checked all my settings and all the volume options are turned up. this happened before I updated to Android 10 tonight and I'm stumped. I have a pixel 2xl
